{"tid":673074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勁多圖]天文台調高佛誕市區高溫預測至34°C 後日改料35°C","createTime":"2018-05-21T13:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T06:55:39.000Z","uid":160147,"like":281,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"1081d892998acaaf0e166636c4afd59fb67173a4","tid":673074,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"天文台原先預計，市區在明日佛誕（22日）和後日，將分別高達33和34&deg;C，惟今日下午4時半，天文台調高這兩日的氣溫預測，分別改料34和35&deg;C。此外，天文台原先亦預計酷熱天氣（33&deg;C或以上）僅持續至後日，但今早11時半亦更改預測，預計酷熱天氣會延至下周日（27日）才結束，較早前的預測還要多4日。<br />\n<br />\n截至今日，天文台已連續5日錄得33&deg;C或以上，是歷來5月第二長的酷熱天氣，僅次於1963年的連續8日。本港多個海灘連日均吸引大批市民前往消暑。天文台指，本港正受一股高空反氣旋支配，連日晴朗、少雲少雨，隨着一道低壓槽會在下周初為華南沿岸帶來驟雨，本港的暑熱天氣才有望稍為紓緩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526904686_a125.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526904686_a125.png&h=42d29345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原相由夏家朗攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902201_8737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902201_8737.jpg&h=f33b0f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天文台原先預計，市區在明日佛誕（22日）和後日，將分別高達33和34&deg;C，惟今日下午4時半，天文台調高這兩日的氣溫預測，分別改料34和35&deg;C。（夏家朗攝 )<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902204_ce67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902204_ce67.jpg&h=42fdf523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天文台預計酷熱天氣會延至下周日（27日）才結束，較早前的預測還要多4日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902439_c232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902439_c232.jpg&h=02f5b26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連日天氣酷熱，吸引不少人到海灘消暑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902441_0160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902441_0160.jpg&h=3fe289d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n截至今日，天文台已連續5日錄得33&deg;C或以上，是歷來5月第二長的酷熱天氣，僅次於1963年的連續8日。（夏家朗攝 ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902444_9cbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902444_9cbf.jpg&h=5896b80f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天文台指，本港正受一股高空反氣旋支配，連日晴朗、少雲少雨。（夏家朗攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902449_6bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902449_6bff.jpg&h=3e6c1685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨着一道低壓槽會在下周初為華南沿岸帶來驟雨，本港的暑熱天氣才有望稍為紓緩。（夏家朗攝 ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902689_cc3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902689_cc3b.jpg&h=e6bb26a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏家朗攝 <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902692_2565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902692_2565.jpg&h=8433330c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏家朗攝 <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902695_aa3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902695_aa3a.jpg&h=33181030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏家朗攝 <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902698_1dba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902698_1dba.jpg&h=8f8a331b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏家朗攝 <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526902700_9a4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526902700_9a4a.jpg&h=9f86d623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏家朗攝"},{"pid":"30eb379bd59e23033e838ae8fb8aee08ee00a550","tid":673074,"uid":143026,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:48:54.000Z","msg":"真係勁多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21cedcce8f0eba7da36f46fdde09a62a6a22271","tid":673074,"uid":31203,"like":401,"dislike":3,"score":398,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"夏家朗攝"},{"pid":"50e54916bab7d15a6e5ba3422fdccaad6a834b0b","tid":673074,"uid":103310,"like":245,"dislike":3,"score":242,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"夏家朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656379f7f0a35d5c1d508d72a6d7f1eb592ad15b","tid":673074,"uid":102096,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2a63b015b8d63b0ed1b2c41087f09f1ad8ac7ac","tid":673074,"uid":2419,"like":336,"dislike":5,"score":331,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"夏家朗死咸濕仔"},{"pid":"582ac8ceda0282d17258e9795c09b52d32a7e2b3","tid":673074,"uid":21917,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"圖片與標題無咩關係 不過無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0744096e6c3a9b2c447085c8c47912cdec4a68","tid":673074,"uid":47112,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"夏家朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e8e414e6e0a374296dfb501e8978104